    <div class="container marketing">

      <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
      <div class="row belonging-means">
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">What does "belonging" mean to others?</h2>
        <h5 class="sectionTitle">We interviewed students, parents, educators and researchers to find out what belonging means to them. Here’s what they told us:</h5>
        <div id="whatCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <!-- Indicators -->


          <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
          <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
            <div class="item active">
             <div class="col-lg-6">
              <%= image_tag "welcome/danyelle.jpg", class: "slider-profile", alt: ""%>
              <h3 class="belonging-intro-name">Danyelle Durall, DC parent & educator</h3>
              <p><span class="belonging-intro-quote">Belonging is:</span>  When my children and students have the same access & aspirations as their peers, whether black, white, or Hispanic</p>

            </div><!-- /.col-lg-6 -->
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <%= image_tag "welcome/Jonathan.jpg", class: "slider-profile", alt: "" %>
              <h3 class="belonging-intro-name" >Jonathan Rivers, DC school social worker</h3>
              <p><span class="belonging-intro-quote">Belonging is:</span>  Absolutely essential for students to feel that they are able to grow and trust.</p>

            </div><!-- /.col-lg-6 -->
          </div>

          <div class="item">
           <div class="col-lg-6">
            <%= image_tag "welcome/Mai.jpg", class: "slider-profile", alt: "" %>
            <h3 class="belonging-intro-name">Mai S., San Francisco student</h3>
            <p><span class="belonging-intro-quote">Belonging is:</span>  People accepting me as a black muslim girl and acknowledging me as a regular human being</p>

          </div><!-- /.col-lg-6 -->

          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <%= image_tag "welcome/Jada.jpg", class: "slider-profile", alt: "" %>
            <h3 class="belonging-intro-name">Jada P., DC student</h3>
            <p><span class="belonging-intro-quote">Belonging is:</span>  A place where you are supposed to be and where you are needed</p>

          </div><!-- /.col-lg-6 -->

        </div>

        <div class="item">
         <div class="col-lg-6">

          <%= image_tag "welcome/Paige.jpg", class: "slider-profile", alt: "" %>
          <h3 class="belonging-intro-name">Paige Hoffman, DC Public Schools staff</h3>
          <p><span class="belonging-intro-quote">Belonging is:</span> When the weight of the world and all the expectations people have of you just come off</p>

        </div><!-- /.col-lg-6 -->

        <div class="col-lg-6">

          <%= image_tag "welcome/William.jpg", class: "slider-profile", alt: "" %>
          <h3 class="belonging-intro-name">William Gardener, DC uncle</h3>
          <p> <span class="belonging-intro-quote">Belonging is:</span> Being a productive part of my community where we all work together to educate our children</p>

        </div><!-- /.col-lg-6 -->

